(10009, 'High-rise Dish Nickel', 0, 0, 'High-rise Elevated Dog Feeders: Polished Nickel Finish- Design in its purest form, this contemporary High-rise collection of elevated porcelain feeders features a shiny nickel finish. The High-rise feeders provide a stylish accent to your home and your pet''s dining experience.', 1, 10000, ''),
