(30001, 'The Wobble Ball', 685, 0.31, 'Your pup loves to play, and there is nothing more exciting than when food is part of the equation! The P.L.A.Y. Wobble Ball Toy is a treat dispensing toy which will provide hours of interactive fun and enrichment for your dog. It is designed with strong threading to allow parts to be easily cleaned and to stay secure when in use. The wobble ball comes with 3 cloud-shaped openings for easy insertion and removal of treats. Simply put a treat in and reward your dog for their persistence and intelligence! \r\n\r\nThe Wobble Ball Toy is not a chew or fetch toy,but a fun interactive play toy for your pup. Supervise your dog while playing. If you have an aggressive chewer, we do not recommend this toy.', 5, 10002, ''),
