(50012, 'Snuggle Bed (3)', 0, 0, 'Sewn with dirt-resistant canvas on one side and luxurious faux fur on the other, this convertible dog bed can be molded into a variety of shapes and uses, conforming to you and your pet''s lifestyle, and offering your pup or kitty a heavenly retreat.</li><li> Furniture-grade craftsmanship and even-basting stitching ensures dog-years of use</li><li>Made in a facility that meets the strict quality standards for infant and children products', 5, 10004, ''),
(40005, 'Graffiti star trainer', 0, 0, 'Casual and stylish. The top features a soft weave and star pattern for a bold statement. The cut and soft fabric allow for a smooth, comfortable fit.', 7, 10003, ''),
(40006, 'Color block trainer', 0, 0, 'Casual and stylish. Comfortable, easy-in, easy-out one-button collar.The top is made to give your pet extra warmth. The cut and soft fabric allow for a smooth, comfortable fit.', 7, 10003, ''),
(40007, 'Crack skull Parker top (moscape)', 0, 0, 'Get a rough look with a hoodie in skull pattern . Stylish, comfortable, easy-in, easy-out one-button collar. Made of high-tech fabric, "Moscape", which is anti-mosquito / tick / flea, incorporating mint and eucalyptus, cypress component, helping prevent such diseases as heart worm, flea allergic dermatitis, that caused by mosquito n fleas. Recommended on a hot day.', 7, 10003, ''),
(40008, 'Polar bear star knit top', 0, 0, 'Casual and stylish. Comfortable, easy-in, easy-out one-button collar.The top is made to give your pet extra warmth. The cut and soft fabric allow for a smooth, comfortable fit.', 7, 10003, ''),
(40009, 'Tribal fleece top', 0, 0, 'Casual and stylish. Comfortable, easy-in, easy-out one-button collar.The top is made to give your pet extra warmth. The cut and soft fabric allow for a smooth, comfortable fit. Water-repellent. Suitable for outdoor activities.', 7, 10003, '');
